[https://github.com/emacs-lsp/lsp-mode lsp-mode] is a client for LanguageServerProtocol. It "aims to provide IDE-like experience by providing optional integration with the most popular Emacs packages like [CompanyMode company], Flycheck and Projectile.".

It supports using dozens of different language servers, [https://emacs-lsp.github.io/lsp-mode/page/languages/ which see].
